\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down transition-transform duration-200\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></a></div><div class=\"relative group\"><a class=\"text-sm font-medium text-foreground/80 hover:text-electric-blue transition-colors flex items-center gap-1 uppercase tracking-wider\" href=\"/portfolio\">Company<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down transition-transform duration-200\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></a></div><a class=\"bg-electric-blue text-white px-6 py-2 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider hover:bg-electric-blue-lt transition-colors rounded-sm\" href=\"/contact\">Get Started</a></div><button class=\"lg:hidden text-white\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 5h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 12h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 19h16\"></path></svg></button></div></nav><main class=\"flex-grow\"><div class=\"relative pt-32 pb-32 space-y-32 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 z-0 pointer-events-none opacity-50\"><div style=\"position:relative;width:100%;height:100%;overflow:hidden;pointer-events:auto\"><div style=\"width:100%;height:100%\"><canvas style=\"display:block\"></canvas></div></div></div><section class=\"relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 text-center\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-electric-blue font-bold mb-6\">Our Mission</div><h1 class=\"text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold text-white tracking-tighter leading-tight mb-8\">Building Brands That <span class=\"text-electric-blue\">Dominate</span></h1><p class=\"text-grey text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed\">Hephzibah Media is Nigeria&#x27;s premium digital marketing, tech, and print agency. We combine local market fluency with international technical standards to deliver growth-oriented digital ecosystems.</p></div></section><section class=\"relative z-10 bg-midnight-mid/80 backdrop-blur-sm py-20 border-y border-white/5\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12\"><div class=\"text-center\"><div class=\"text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-electric-blue mb-2\">12+</div><div class=\"text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-grey font-bold\">Years Experience</div></div><div class=\"text-center\"><div class=\"text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-electric-blue mb-2\">36</div><div class=\"text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-grey font-bold\">States Served</div></div><div class=\"text-center\"><div class=\"text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-electric-blue mb-2\">98%</div><div class=\"text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-grey font-bold\">Client Retention</div></div></div></section><section class=\"relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6\"><div class=\"mb-16 text-center\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-4 justify-center\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:none\"><span class=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-electric-blue font-bold\">Our Values</span><span class=\"w-8 h-[1px] bg-electric-blue ml-4\"></span></div><h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6 tracking-tight leading-tight\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">What We <span class=\"text-electric-blue\">Stand For</span></h2><p class=\"text-grey text-lg max-w-2xl leading-relaxed mx-auto\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">We operate with a core set of principles that ensure our clients receive the highest level of service and results.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-1 mt-16\"><div class=\"glass p-12 border border-white/5 hover:border-electric-blue/30 transition-all\"><div class=\"text-electric-blue mb-6\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-target\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"6\"></circle><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 tracking-tight\">Strategy Before Execution</h3><p class=\"text-grey leading-relaxed\">We never touch a keyboard without a clear brief, agreed KPIs, and a strategy both parties believe in.</p></div><div class=\"glass p-12 border border-white/5 hover:border-electric-blue/30 transition-all\"><div class=\"text-electric-blue mb-6\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-message-square\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M22 17a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6.828a2 2 0 0 0-1.414.586l-2.202 2.202A.71.71 0 0 1 2 21.286V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h16a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 tracking-tight\">Nigerian Market Fluency</h3><p class=\"text-grey leading-relaxed\">We understand 3G constraints, WhatsApp culture, payment friction, and what makes Nigerians trust a brand online.</p></div><div class=\"glass p-12 border border-white/5 hover:border-electric-blue/30 transition-all\"><div class=\"text-electric-blue mb-6\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-zap\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 tracking-tight\">Radical Transparency</h3><p class=\"text-grey leading-relaxed\">Monthly reports, open access to analytics, and honest conversations when something isn&#x27;t working.</p></div><div class=\"glass p-12 border border-white/5 hover:border-electric-blue/30 transition-all\"><div class=\"text-electric-blue mb-6\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 tracking-tight\">Ownership Mindset</h3><p class=\"text-grey leading-relaxed\">Your success is our portfolio. We treat every project as if our name is on the outcome — because it is.</p></div></div></section></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"bg-midnight-mid border-t border-white/10 pt-20 pb-10\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-12 mb-16\"><div class=\"space-y-6\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-3 group\" href=\"/\"><div class=\"relative w-8 h-8 overflow-hidden\"><img alt=\"Hephzibah Media Logo\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-contain group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2FHephzibah%20Media%20Logo.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2FHephzibah%20Media%20Logo.png&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?ur